    "# Ekman Emotion Classification — Single-Stage E2E\n",
    "\n",
    "**Task**: 7-class multi-label classification (6 emotions + neutral)  \n",
    "**Models**: DeBERTa / RoBERTa / ELECTRA / BERT  \n",
    "**Output**: `run_e2e/<model_name>/` on Google Drive\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "### Folder structure expected\n",
    "```\n",
    "MyDrive/\n",
    "  your_project/\n",
    "    src/\n",
    "      dataloader.py\n",
    "      train.py\n",
    "      test.py\n",
    "      utils.py\n",
    "    models/\n",
    "      loss.py\n",
    "    config/\n",
    "      config.yaml\n",
    "    data/\n",
    "      data1_train.csv\n",
    "      data1_val.csv\n",
    "      data1_test.csv\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
